metadata.title: Risultati Unificati da sourcetype stream:ip
metadata.description: Contiene tutti i risultati alle query svolte per stream:ip

data.Query: index=botsv3 sourcetype=stream:ip | stats sum(bytes) as total_bytes by protocol | where total_bytes > 5
index=botsv3 sourcetype=stream:ip | stats count by protocol
index=botsv3 sourcetype=stream:ip | stats count AS value by src_ip, dest_ip | eval tooltip = "SRC: " . src_ip . " | DEST: " . dest_ip . " | COUNT: " . value| table value tooltip src_ip dest_ip
index=botsv3 source=stream:ip | stats avg(bytes) AS Media, median(bytes) AS Mediana, stdev(bytes) AS Deviazione_Standard| table source,Media, Mediana, Deviazione_Standard

index=botsv3 sourcetype=stream:ip | timechart span=1m count | streamstats avg(count) as avg stdev(count) as stdev| eval upper_bound = avg + 2*stdev, lower_bound = avg - 2*stdev| table _time, count, lower_bound, upper_bound
index=botsv3 sourcetype=stream:ip | stats count by src_ip  | sort -count | head 15
